- Hey.<br>
- Hey.
<SYNC Start=820277><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=823722><P Class=ENCC>
Once we're in the air and the<br>
captain turns off the seat belt sign..
<SYNC Start=827055><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=827226><P Class=ENCC>
you feel free to roam about my cabin.
<SYNC Start=830286><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
