<SYNC Start=882713><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=883215><P Class=ENCC>
I'll tell her that it's over<br>
tonight at dinner. I promise.
<SYNC Start=886082><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
