I know.
<SYNC Start=937096><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=937269><P Class=ENCC>
Well, if that's the case,<br>
I just want you to know..
<SYNC Start=939760><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=939939><P Class=ENCC>
that I think I could have fallen for you<br>
really, really hard.
<SYNC Start=943602><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=944910><P Class=ENCC>
On the other hand,<br>
if he is okay with us..
<SYNC Start=948437><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=948914><P Class=ENCC>
then, you know, it's cas, whatever.
<SYNC Start=950848><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=955087><P Class=ENCC>
Ross is coming over. I think now<br>
would be a good time to talk to him.
<SYNC Start=958420><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=959224><P Class=ENCC>
I guess so. I'm just..<br>
I'm really nervous.
<SYNC Start=961818><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=961994><P Class=ENCC>
Well, keep in mind<br>
that by the time you're done..
<SYNC Start=964394><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=964563><P Class=ENCC>
they'll probably be serving dinner.
<SYNC Start=967327><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
