- Yeah?<br>
- Last night, after you guys broke up..
<SYNC Start=998553><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=998731><P Class=ENCC>
So sorry to hear about that,<br>
by the way.
<SYNC Start=1002098><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1003068><P Class=ENCC>
Well, Charlie and I were talking, and..
<SYNC Start=1007903><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1008807><P Class=ENCC>
Well..
<SYNC Start=1010638><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1011176><P Class=ENCC>
You kissed.
<SYNC Start=1012507><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1012678><P Class=ENCC>
Wh.. What?
<SYNC Start=1017138><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1017316><P Class=ENCC>
What? What would give you that idea?
<SYNC Start=1020342><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1020519><P Class=ENCC>
- I saw you.<br>
- Yeah, we kissed.
<SYNC Start=1023147><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1024523><P Class=ENCC>
But nothing else.<br>
Nothing else happened, okay?
<SYNC Start=1028550><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1028761><P Class=ENCC>
- Ross, Ross, Ross. It's okay.<br>
- What?
<SYNC Start=1031821><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
