You guys..
<SYNC Start=1037827><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1038037><P Class=ENCC>
make way more sense than her<br>
and I ever did, you know? And..
<SYNC Start=1042804><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1042975><P Class=ENCC>
- I want you to be happy.<br>
- Are you serious?
<SYNC Start=1046172><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1046345><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah.
<SYNC Start=1047903><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1050582><P Class=ENCC>
- Now I have something..<br>
- I am speechless.
<SYNC Start=1053847><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1055187><P Class=ENCC>
I mean, the fact that you would put<br>
my happiness first like that, I mean..
<SYNC Start=1059886><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1060092><P Class=ENCC>
You're an incredible friend,<br>
do you know that?
<SYNC Start=1062526><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1062728><P Class=ENCC>
- Well, look, before you go..<br>
- No, I mean it.
<SYNC Start=1065390><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1065597><P Class=ENCC>
I mean, you're so loyal, man.<br>
And selfless and generous.
<SYNC Start=1072264><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1073105><P Class=ENCC>
I am those things, yeah.
<SYNC Start=1074868><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1075607><P Class=ENCC>
I've known Chandler longer, so I think<br>
