<SYNC Start=1081842><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1083215><P Class=ENCC>
I may have to rethink some stuff.
<SYNC Start=1085581><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1086118><P Class=ENCC>
Dude!
<SYNC Start=1087278><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1087486><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, if there is ever anything<br>
