<SYNC Start=1091786><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1094126><P Class=ENCC>
I can't think of anything.
<SYNC Start=1095821><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1098530><P Class=ENCC>
- Thanks.<br>
- Yeah.
<SYNC Start=1100623><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1104870><P Class=ENCC>
- So hi.<br>
- Hi.
<SYNC Start=1106201><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1106371><P Class=ENCC>
- So you talked to Joey?<br>
- Oh, yeah. We had a really good talk.
<SYNC Start=1110705><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1110876><P Class=ENCC>
- Oh, that's great.<br>
- Yeah.
<SYNC Start=1112776><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1112945><P Class=ENCC>
- So everything's okay?<br>
- Oh, no, it's great.
<SYNC Start=1115880><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1116048><P Class=ENCC>
- It's great. He's an amazing guy.<br>
- Oh, well, obviously, I think so too.
<SYNC Start=1121543><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1122054><P Class=ENCC>
Well, I'm so excited about this.
<SYNC Start=1124852><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1126225><P Class=ENCC>
Really? Excited?
<SYNC Start=1129194><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1129361><P Class=ENCC>
What, are you kidding? I have had<br>
