<SYNC Start=1134890><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1138070><P Class=ENCC>
Excuse me.
<SYNC Start=1140265><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1146178><P Class=ENCC>
