<SYNC Start=1156418><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1157189><P Class=ENCC>
Fine. Forget it. When we go back<br>
to New York, I will tell him.
<SYNC Start=1160420><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1160592><P Class=ENCC>
Thank you. Yeah, I appreciate that.
<SYNC Start=1162389><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1181847><P Class=ENCC>
- Hi, Mike's place.<br>
- Hey, it's Mike.
<SYNC Start=1184247><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1184449><P Class=ENCC>
- That was fast.<br>
- Oh, no, she's not here yet.
<SYNC Start=1187111><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1187953><P Class=ENCC>
You know, I'm just gonna take off<br>
