<SYNC Start=1191719><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1191890><P Class=ENCC>
You can't do that. Oh, come on, Mike,<br>
strap on a pair.
<SYNC Start=1195451><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1197462><P Class=ENCC>
