<SYNC Start=1263823><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1265564><P Class=ENCC>
- You go back to work tomorrow night?<br>
- Yeah.
<SYNC Start=1267828><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1268033><P Class=ENCC>
So if you want people to see them..
<SYNC Start=1270001><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1270168><P Class=ENCC>
you're not having them taken out,<br>
say, at the break of dawn?
<SYNC Start=1273160><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1273839><P Class=ENCC>
Well, if I had them taken out,<br>
then I wouldn't be able to do this.
<SYNC Start=1277400><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1284149><P Class=ENCC>
You like that, right?
<SYNC Start=1286379><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1293525><P Class=ENCC>
- What are you singing?<br>
- It's "Bolero" from 10.
<SYNC Start=1296722><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1296928><P Class=ENCC>
It's "Ride of the Valkyries"<br>
