<SYNC Start=1304801><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1304970><P Class=ENCC>
Now that we're home, you don't have<br>
that problem. If you think about it..
<SYNC Start=1308565><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1308740><P Class=ENCC>
I hate them.
<SYNC Start=1310605><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
