<SYNC Start=1340571><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1340739><P Class=ENCC>
You're just jealous<br>
because your hair can't do this.
<SYNC Start=1344072><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1347212><P Class=ENCC>
