<SYNC Start=1349703><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1358990><P Class=ENCC>
Hi! There she is! Hi, Emma.<br>
Oh, my God, I missed you.
<SYNC Start=1364929><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1365130><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, Emma, I missed you so much. Hi.
<SYNC Start=1368156><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1368333><P Class=ENCC>
